<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <hi rend="grantha">tribhuva</hi>ṉac cakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">jādh</hi>[<hi rend="grantha">i</hi>]<hi rend="grantha">rājad</hi>evaṟku yāṇṭu Añcā
<lb n="2"/>vatu kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu<hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>yañ ciṟupaḻuvūr Uṭaiyār tiruvālaṉtuṟaiyuṭai
<lb n="3"/>ya nāyaṉāṟku Ivvūr Irukkum Ampaṉatti viṟṟiruṉtāṉ pañcanetikkup pukka<unclear>moka</unclear>ṉ
<lb n="4"/>Āṇṭatiru Ivaṉ Ennakamuṭaiyānum I<unclear>va</unclear>ṉ Uṭaṉ piṟaṉtā<unclear>nu</unclear>m A<hi rend="grantha">bhā</hi>vattu <unclear>Eṉnu</unclear>tā
<lb n="5"/>y varukiṟa Ikkuṉṟakkūṟṟattuk kiḻkkuṟṟil <unclear>Am</unclear> Araikkāṇiyil Eṉ Akamuṭaiyaṉ eṭa<unclear>t</unclear>tuk kū
<lb n="6"/>ṟu Araiyum Ivaṉ Uṭaṉ piṟaṉta <unclear>E</unclear>ṉ koḻu<unclear>ṉ</unclear>taṉ tiruvālaṉtuṟai kāṇiyāṉa opātiyil I
<lb n="7"/>vaṉ viṟṟutu kāle Araikkāl kūṟu pokki Itukku commāy <unclear>I</unclear>vaṉ A<hi rend="grantha">bhā</hi>vattu Eṉṉuṭāy varu
<lb n="8"/>kiṟa kūṟu Araikkāl Āka Araiyey araikkāl paṟṟālum Uḷḷa Irāvirukkaiyum yā<unclear>ḻ</unclear>pāṭṭuk kiḻipā
<lb n="9"/>ṭṭu piḷavūrkkavāl cappāṉi Uḷḷiṭṭu Am<unclear>pa</unclear>ṉattoḻilāl Eṅkaḷiṉ avar cey toḻil Eppeṟpaṭṭu
<lb n="10"/><unclear>tum</unclear> Ittiruvālaṉtuṟai <unclear>U</unclear>ṭaiya nāyaṉāṟkut tirumeṟ pūccukkuṭalāka <unclear>I</unclear>ṉṉ<unclear>ā</unclear>ya<unclear>ṉā</unclear>r<hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> pāttu n<unclear>ir</unclear>varttuk ku {few letters not legible}
<lb n="11"/>n <unclear>I</unclear>nta Aṇṭa<unclear>ta</unclear>ruveṉ ||
</p>

